# Authors — llama-forge

## Fork maintainer

Sumit (dev-boffin-io) <https://github.com/dev-boffin-io>

## Fork-specific additions

The following components are original to this fork and not part of upstream llama.cpp:

- `llama_gui/` — native Linux desktop GUI (Chat, Quantize, Convert Tools)
- `llama_gui/CMakeLists.txt` — PyInstaller build system + desktop entry install
- `llama_gui/core/` — project root detection, quant logic, converter logic
- `llama_gui/gui/` — Tkinter UI components
- `llama_gui/utils/` — terminal detection, subprocess streaming, GGUF info reader, RAM detection

## Upstream contributors

This fork is built on [llama.cpp](https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp) by the ggml-org community.
The full list of upstream contributors is maintained at:

  https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp/blob/master/AUTHORS

All credit for the core inference engine, quantization tools, conversion scripts,
and everything outside of `llama_gui/` belongs to the upstream contributors.
